<section class="ai-section" id="ai">
  <div class="section-header" style="padding: 0 0 30px;">
    <div class="section-num">— 05 / AI in the Pipeline</div>
    <h2>ART DIRECTED <em>THEN GENERATED</em></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="ai-intro">
    <div class="ai-copy">
      <p>We work with the sharpest generative tools in the industry — Midjourney, Seedance, Nano Banana, Runway, and more — to move briefs from reference to moving concept frames in hours, not weeks.</p>
      <p class="dim">AI isn't the pitch. It's the draftsman. Every frame is curated, art-directed, and shaped to the director's intent — so what you get is a treatment with a real visual language, not a mood board of model outputs.</p>
      <div class="ai-tools">
        <span class="ai-tool">Midjourney</span>
        <span class="ai-tool">Seedance</span>
        <span class="ai-tool">Nano Banana</span>
        <span class="ai-tool">Runway</span>
        <span class="ai-tool">Sora</span>
        <span class="ai-tool">Kling</span>
        <span class="ai-tool">Luma</span>
        <span class="ai-tool">+ more</span>
      </div>
    </div>
